{"tid":2478921,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"壽司郎：香港單店銷售額達日本店2倍，今年9月前會大幅擴充","createTime":"2021-04-07T12:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T13:56:51.000Z","uid":158504,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8a558db189461b558af9d039192c4056d40ad3","tid":2478921,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"日本迴轉壽司店「壽司郎」在香港颳起旋風<br />\n2021/04/07<br />\n在香港，由日本Sushiro Global Holdings經營的壽司郎連日來年輕顧客盈門。香港的單店銷售額達到日本店舖的2倍。Sushiro公司還計劃借助香港的人氣進駐中國大陸<br />\n<br />\n壽司郎2020財年（截至2020年9月）在香港新開了4家店。2021財年（截至2021年9月）也計劃開設7～9家店，4月將在香港島的商務區開設上環店。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/tradingretail/44241-2021-04-07-05-00-34.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Ftradingretail%2F44241-2021-04-07-05-00-34.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=164a697d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/tradingretail/44241-2021-04-07-05-00-34.html</a><br />\n<br />\n4+9=13，計返連埋上環 葵芳 total已知嘅有9間<br />\n<br />\n<strong>即係仲有4個地方有機會中獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"6b81fb831080ec528b85b28431183e99bf5153a8","tid":2478921,"uid":150466,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"一定有荃灣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4974b54c663d2c6ec612d3f5e7711ee4b37cebb0","tid":2478921,"uid":143452,"like":18,"dislike":15,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"準備收皮啦 咁撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做返好似開業嗰排個水準先再擴張啦"},{"pid":"c70b1b1059e266377b62d0138cb6c999db3804ed","tid":2478921,"uid":131551,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"唔係要返去奶共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壽司郎再擴充　計劃廣東省開店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2342667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2342667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a9e9e47935c4adfeab20af62cf5ae8bd7d05299","tid":2478921,"uid":178875,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"夠薑就去美食沙漠馬鞍山開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到佢開24都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3454b10f1fe11a7adf89cc0cb1bccad8e90a42","tid":2478921,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"虛火黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cdd00951b930b98e539d0d1775dc0e3754ab53","tid":2478921,"uid":158504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a9e9e47935c4adfeab20af62cf5ae8bd7d05299","tid":2478921,"uid":178875,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"夠薑就去美食沙漠馬鞍山開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到佢開24都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"計漏大埔<br />\n應該有3個地方有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d72da8142174eb9b095cf134e02320ff108b9b","tid":2478921,"uid":372763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本食過一次，舊舊飯都甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港冇打算去食"},{"pid":"0f1a27a63c5b3f2b7292e3bb67ca4f4182464c27","tid":2478921,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4974b54c663d2c6ec612d3f5e7711ee4b37cebb0","tid":2478921,"uid":143452,"like":18,"dislike":15,"score":3,"cit